<div id="txtcont" class="span9" style="position: relative;">
    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-1a' );" name="005-1a" class="pb">[005-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:189'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='189:198'>　周禮述註卷五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='198:218'>　　　　　　　　　　　　安溪李光坡撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='218:241'>○九嬪掌婦學之灋以敎九御婦徳婦言婦容婦功各</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='241:254'>帥其屬而以時御敘于王所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='254:277'>　註曰婦徳謂貞順婦言謂辭令婦容謂婉娩婦功謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='277:300'>　絲枲自九嬪以下九九而御于王所九嬪者既習于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='300:323'>　四事又備于從人之道是以敎女御也敎各帥其屬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='323:349'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-1b' );" name="005-1b" class="pb">[005-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='349:372'>　者使亦九九相與從于王所息之燕寢御猶進也勸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='372:395'>　也進勸王息亦相次敘凡羣妃御見之灋月與后妃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='395:418'>　其象也卑者宜先尊者宜後女御八十一人當九夕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='418:441'>　世婦二十七人當三夕九嬪九人當一夕三夫人當</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='441:464'>　一夕后當一夕亦十五日而徧云自望後反之孔子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='464:487'>　云日者天之明月者地之理陰契制故月上屬為天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='487:510'>　使婦從夫放月紀　娩音晚見賢遍反上時掌反放</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='510:516'>　方往反</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='516:542'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-2a' );" name="005-2a" class="pb">[005-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='542:556'>凡祭祀贊玉齍贊后薦徹豆籩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='556:579'>　註曰玉齍玉敦受黍稷器后進之而不徹　疏曰助</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='579:600'>　后薦玉齍也豆籩之薦與徹皆助后　敦音對</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='600:609'>若有賓客則從后</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='609:632'>　註曰當贊后事　疏曰后之有事于賓客者唯諸侯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='632:646'>　來朝王親饗燕之后當從王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='646:657'>大喪帥敘哭者亦如之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='657:678'>　註曰亦從后帥猶道也后哭之衆次敘者乃哭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='678:704'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-2b' );" name="005-2b" class="pb">[005-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='704:727'>○世婦掌祭祀賓客喪紀之事帥女宫而濯摡為齍盛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='727:750'>　註曰摡拭也為猶差擇　疏曰案少牢饔人摡鼎俎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='750:773'>　廩人摡甑甗司宫摡豆籩彼以大夫家無婦官及無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='773:788'>　刑女故并使男子官此天子禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='788:806'>○及祭之日涖陳女宫之具凡内羞之物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='806:829'>　註曰涖者臨也内羞謂房中之羞　疏曰案春官世</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='829:852'>　婦宫卿云掌女宫之宿戒及祭祀比其具此官直臨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='852:868'>　之而已　摡古愛反註同拭音式</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='868:894'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-3a' );" name="005-3a" class="pb">[005-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='894:905'>掌弔臨于卿大夫之喪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='905:928'>　註曰王使往弔　疏曰案司服公卿大夫皆王親弔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='928:951'>　之此文使世婦往弔者此盖使世婦致禮物但弔是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='951:974'>　大名雖致禮亦名為弔此所弔不言三公與孤者文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='974:980'>　不具也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='980:993'>○女御掌御敘于王之燕寢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='993:1016'>　註曰言掌御敘防上之専妬者于王之燕寢則王不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1016:1024'>　就后宫息也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1024:1050'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-3b' );" name="005-3b" class="pb">[005-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1050:1058'>以歲時獻功事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1058:1069'>　註曰絲枲成功之事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1069:1077'>凡祭祀贊世婦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1077:1088'>　註曰助其帥涖女宫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1088:1095'>大喪掌沐浴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1095:1118'>　註曰王及后之喪　疏曰王及后喪沐用潘浴用湯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1118:1141'>　始死為之于南牖下但男子不死于婦人之手今王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1141:1164'>　喪亦使女御浴者案士喪禮浴時男子抗衾則不使</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1164:1190'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-4a' );" name="005-4a" class="pb">[005-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1190:1213'>　婦人今王喪沐或使婦人而浴未必婦人或亦供給</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1213:1233'>　湯物而已亦得謂之掌也　潘鋪官切音拌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1233:1240'>后之喪持翣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1240:1263'>　翣棺飾也漢禮翣方扇以木為匡廣二尺兩角高二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1263:1286'>　尺四寸柄長五尺以布覆之天子八翣后同女御持</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1286:1305'>　而從柩車左右各四人　翣所甲反後同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1305:1318'>從世婦而弔于卿大夫之喪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1318:1341'>　註曰從之數盖如使者之介云　疏曰王之妃妾夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1341:1367'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-4b' );" name="005-4b" class="pb">[005-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1367:1390'>　人象公嬪象孤卿世婦象大夫女御象元士但介數</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1390:1411'>　依命數為差王之大夫四命世婦之從亦四人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1411:1429'>○女祝掌王后之内祭祀凡内禱祠之事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1429:1452'>　註曰内祭祀六宫之中竈門戸禱疾病求瘳也祠報</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1452:1475'>　福　疏曰月令春祀戸夏祀竈秋祀門后祀之時亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1475:1494'>　當依此也婦人無外事無行與中霤之等</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1494:1509'>掌以時招梗禬禳之事以除疾殃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1509:1532'>　疏曰以時者謂隨其事時不必要在四時也招謂招</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1532:1558'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-5a' );" name="005-5a" class="pb">[005-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1558:1581'>　取善祥梗禦捍惡之未至也除災害曰禬禬猶刮也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1581:1604'>　刮去見在之災禳攘也推卻見在之變異　陳君舉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1604:1627'>　曰胡五峯謂宫闈不當有此是盖未察先王之意古</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1627:1650'>　人通天人徹幽明動則有祭故食則祭先食桑則祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1650:1673'>　先蠶農則祭先嗇與夫門行户竈表貉先牧馬祖等</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1673:1696'>　類不一不唯不忘初之意盖神所在有之故所在祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1696:1719'>　之皆先王謹微之意所以自盡焉外朝有司巫男巫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1719:1742'>　女巫内朝有女祝所掌者大氐類後世淫祀祈望非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1742:1768'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-5b' );" name="005-5b" class="pb">[005-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1768:1791'>　福然先王不以為不可必設官以掌之者交三才之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1791:1814'>　道也若曰人事既盡此等事一切勿講則非聖人之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1814:1837'>　意　梗古猛反禬古外反禳如羊反貉與禡同音罵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1837:1848'>　朝直遙反氐古抵字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1848:1859'>○女史掌王后之禮職</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1859:1882'>　王光逺曰王后之禮各有所職若祭祀則有薦徹賓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1882:1896'>　禮則有獻酬其職女史掌之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1896:1909'>掌内治之貳以詔后治内政</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1909:1935'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-6a' );" name="005-6a" class="pb">[005-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1935:1952'>　註曰内治之灋本在内宰書而貳之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1952:1957'>逆内宫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1957:1980'>　逆内宫者謂六宫所有功事及費用財物粟米皆鉤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='1980:1985'>　攷之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='1985:1990'>書内令</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='1990:2005'>　内令后令也書而宣布于六宫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2005:2014'>凡后之事以禮從</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2014:2037'>　疏曰太史以書協禮事執書以詔王此女史亦執禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2037:2063'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-6b' );" name="005-6b" class="pb">[005-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2063:2070'>　書以從后</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2070:2093'>○典婦功掌婦式之灋以授嬪婦及内人女功之事齎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2093:2116'>　註曰婦式婦人事之模範嬪婦九嬪世婦事齎謂以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2116:2139'>　女功之事來取絲枲鄭司農云内人謂女御　坡謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2139:2162'>　内宰以作二事唯據女御不見九嬪世婦有絲枲之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2162:2185'>　事此言嬪婦者盖王后所蠶北郊以為祭服故使嬪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2185:2198'>　婦率先有事焉　齎音咨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2198:2221'>凡授嬪婦功及秋獻功辨其苦良比其小大而賈之物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2221:2247'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-7a' );" name="005-7a" class="pb">[005-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2247:2253'>書而楬之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2253:2276'>　獨舉嬪婦不言内人省文也鄭司農苦讀為盬枲曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2276:2299'>　苦絲曰良而苦良之中人功又有良善觕盬皆當辨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2299:2322'>　之也比方也小大長短廣狹也賈估其直也楬解見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2322:2345'>　職幣上文既言授嬪婦以女功此承之言凡授功者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2345:2368'>　至秋獻功時則分别其縑帛布紵與其觕細皆比方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2368:2383'>　其大小書其賈數而著其物也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2383:2397'>以共王及后之用頒之于内府</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2397:2423'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-7b' );" name="005-7b" class="pb">[005-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2423:2439'>　賈音嫁楬其列反盬音古縑音兼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2439:2462'>　　問授註以當作受如何曰註以嬪婦為國中嬪婦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2462:2485'>　　似與上文牴牾又以國中嬪婦所作成即送之不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2485:2508'>　　須獻功時更于上下文理疑不相蒙且上未嘗言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2508:2531'>　　授國中嬪婦以女功安得突然受其功乎故坡謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2531:2554'>　　凡授嬪婦功此句盖重上文之意以起下文及秋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2554:2577'>　　獻功耳曰苦良司農後鄭異説子兼之何也曰絲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2577:2600'>　　曰良枲曰苦司農為是然以此官不藏布帛而使</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2600:2626'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-8a' );" name="005-8a" class="pb">[005-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2626:2649'>　　典絲主良典枲主苦則于下文頒内府以共王后</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2649:2672'>　　者解將不行後鄭之意則于下文得矣然以此官</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2672:2695'>　　主良則經明兼苦良至改典絲之良為苦又恐牽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2695:2718'>　　合實多坡謂禮言躬桑詩言刈葛宫中所成自有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2718:2741'>　　此苦良二事至典絲之良典枲之苦又自以貢入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2741:2764'>　　之物為之各不相涉也宫中所成藏内府以共王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2764:2787'>　　后貢入所成藏二官以待政令云　牴音底牾音</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2787:2799'>　　吾重直龍反刈音藝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2799:2825'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-8b' );" name="005-8b" class="pb">[005-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2825:2842'>○典絲掌絲入而辨其物以其賈楬之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2842:2865'>　註曰絲入謂九職之嬪婦所貢絲　疏曰后宫所蠶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2865:2888'>　之絲自后宫用之以為祭服不入典絲其歲之常貢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='2888:2911'>　之絲若禹貢兗州貢漆絲之等攷餘官更無絲入之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='2911:2934'>　文亦當入此典絲也物謂絲有善惡麤細不同　賈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='2934:2939'>　音嫁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='2939:2953'>掌其藏與其出以待興功之時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='2953:2976'>　註曰絲之貢少藏之出之可同官也時者若温煖宜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='2976:3002'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-9a' );" name="005-9a" class="pb">[005-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3002:3012'>　縑帛清涼宜文繡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3012:3025'>頒絲于外内工皆以物授之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3025:3048'>　註曰外工外嬪婦也内工女御　疏曰以物授之者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3048:3066'>　若縑帛則授以素絲文繡則授以綵絲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3066:3076'>凡上之賜予亦如之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3076:3087'>　註曰王以絲物賜人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3087:3110'>及獻功則受良功而藏之辨其物而書其數以待有司</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3110:3119'>之政令上之賜予</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3119:3145'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-9b' );" name="005-9b" class="pb">[005-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3145:3168'>　政令謂禮物之幣帛及司服弁師灋物所宜用皆是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3168:3182'>　也鄭司農云良功絲功縑帛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3182:3194'>凡祭祀共黼畫組就之物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3194:3217'>　黼畫衣服及依巾幂也組就以組為就冕旈也白與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3217:3230'>　黑謂之黼采色一成曰就</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3230:3242'>喪紀共其絲纊組文之物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3242:3266'>　絲以給線縷纊以充衣縟組者士喪禮曰握手𤣥纁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3266:3289'>　裏著組繫内則曰屨著綦綦屨繫是用組之事也青</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3289:3316'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-10a' );" name="005-10a" class="pb">[005-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3316:3329'>　與赤謂之文　著直畧反</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3329:3342'>凡飾邦器者受文織絲組焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3342:3354'>　註曰謂茵席屏風之屬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3354:3366'>○歲終則各以其物㑹之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3366:3389'>　註曰種别為計鄭司農云各以其所飾之物計會傅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3389:3405'>　著之　織音志茵音因會古外反</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3405:3428'>○典枲掌布緦縷紵之麻草之物以待時頒功而授齎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3428:3451'>　緦十五升布抽其半者白而細疏曰紵縷綫也麻枲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3451:3478'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-10b' );" name="005-10b" class="pb">[005-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3478:3501'>　苴也草葛䔛之屬授齎謂授給麻草使為布緦縷紵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3501:3512'>　　綫先見反䔛音萌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3512:3531'>及獻功受苦功以其賈楬而藏之以待時頒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3531:3554'>　註曰鄭司農云苦功謂麻功布紵　疏曰以待時頒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3554:3569'>　者即下文頒衣服及賜予是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3569:3582'>○頒衣服授之賜予亦如之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3582:3605'>　註曰授之授受頒者帛言待有司之政令布言頒衣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3605:3615'>　服互文　苦音古</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3615:3642'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-11a' );" name="005-11a" class="pb">[005-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3642:3653'>歲終則各以其物㑹之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='3653:3676'>○内司服掌王后之六服褘衣揄狄闕狄鞠衣展衣緣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='3676:3681'>衣素沙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='3681:3704'>　註曰鄭司農云褘衣畫衣也祭綂曰夫人副褘揄狄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='3704:3727'>　闕狄畫羽飾展衣白衣也喪大記曰復夫人以屈狄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='3727:3750'>　世婦以襢衣屈音與闕相似襢與展相似鞠衣黄衣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='3750:3774'>　也𤣥謂狄當為翟翟雉名伊雒而南素質五色皆備</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='3774:3797'>　成章曰翬江淮而南青質五色皆備成章曰搖王后</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='3797:3824'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-11b' );" name="005-11b" class="pb">[005-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='3824:3847'>　之服刻繒為之形而采畫之綴於衣以為文章褘衣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='3847:3871'>　畫翬者揄翟畫搖者闕翟刻而不畫此三者皆祭服從</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='3871:3894'>　王祭先王則服褘衣祭先公則服揄翟祭羣小祀則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='3894:3917'>　服闕翟今世有圭衣者盖三翟之遺俗鞠衣黄桑服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='3917:3940'>　也色如鞠塵象桑葉始生月令三月薦鞠衣于先帝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='3940:3963'>　告桑事展衣以禮見王及賓客之服字當為襢襢之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='3963:3986'>　言亶亶誠也詩國風曰玼兮玼兮其之翟也下云胡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='3986:4009'>　然而天也胡然而帝也言其徳當神明又曰瑳兮瑳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4009:4036'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-12a' );" name="005-12a" class="pb">[005-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4036:4059'>　兮其之展也下云展如之人兮邦之媛也言其行配</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4059:4082'>　君子二者之義與禮合矣雜記曰夫人服税衣揄狄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4082:4105'>　又喪大記曰士妻以褖衣言褖者甚衆字或作税此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4105:4128'>　緣衣者實作褖衣也褖衣御于王之服亦以燕居男</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4128:4151'>　子之褖衣黑則是亦黑也六服備于此矣褘揄狄展</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4151:4174'>　聲相近緣字之誤也以下推次其色則闕狄赤揄狄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4174:4198'>　青褘衣𤣥婦人尚専一徳無所兼連衣裳不異其色</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4198:4221'>　素沙者今之白縳也六服皆袍制以白縳為裏使之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4221:4248'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-12b' );" name="005-12b" class="pb">[005-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4248:4271'>　張顯今世有沙縠者名出于此　疏曰王之吉服有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4271:4294'>　九韋弁以下常服有三與后鞠衣以下三服同但王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4294:4317'>　之祭服有六后祭服唯三翟者天地山川社稷之等</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4317:4340'>　后夫人不與故三服而已　褘音暉揄音遙展同襢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4340:4363'>　俱張彦反緣同褖俱吐亂反翬音暉見王之見賢遍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4363:4386'>　反亶丹但反玼音此瑳倉我反行下孟反税吐亂反</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4386:4398'>　縳音絹縠音斛與音預</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4398:4415'>辨外内命婦之服鞠衣展衣緣衣素沙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4415:4442'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-13a' );" name="005-13a" class="pb">[005-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4442:4465'>　註曰内命婦之服鞠衣九嬪也展衣世婦也緣衣女</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4465:4488'>　御也外命婦者其夫孤也則服鞠衣其夫卿大夫也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4488:4511'>　則服展衣其夫士也則服緣衣三夫人及公之妻其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4511:4534'>　闕狄以下乎侯伯之夫人搖狄子男之夫人亦闕狄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4534:4543'>　唯二王後褘衣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4543:4566'>凡祭祀賓客共后之衣服及九嬪世婦凡命婦共其衣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4566:4575'>服共喪衰亦如之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4575:4598'>　註曰凡者凡女御與外命婦也言及言凡殊貴賤也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4598:4625'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-13b' );" name="005-13b" class="pb">[005-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='4625:4648'>　春秋之義王人雖微者猶序乎諸侯之上所以尊尊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='4648:4671'>　也臣之命者再命以上受服則下士之妻不共也外</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='4671:4694'>　命婦唯王祭祀賓客以禮佐后得服此上服自于其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='4694:4717'>　家則降焉　疏曰喪衰亦如之者外命婦喪衰為王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='4717:4740'>　服齊衰于后無服若九嬪以下及女御于王服斬衰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='4740:4749'>　于后服齊衰也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='4749:4763'>后之喪共其衣服凡内具之物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='4763:4786'>　註曰内具紛帨線纊鞶袠之屬　疏曰后喪所共衣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='4786:4813'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-14a' );" name="005-14a" class="pb">[005-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='4813:4835'>　服者謂襲時十二稱小斂十九稱大斂百二十稱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='4835:4852'>　帨如鋭反鞶音盤袠陳乙反稱去聲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='4852:4875'>○縫人掌王宫之縫線之事以役女御以縫王及后之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='4875:4879'>衣服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='4879:4902'>　註曰女御裁縫王及后之衣服則為役助之宫中餘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='4902:4919'>　裁縫事則専為之鄭司農云線縷也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='4919:4926'>喪縫棺飾焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='4926:4949'>　註曰孝子既啓見棺猶見親之身既載飾而以行遂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='4949:4976'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-14b' );" name="005-14b" class="pb">[005-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='4976:4999'>　以葬若存時居于帷幕而加文繡喪大記曰飾棺君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='4999:5022'>　龍帷三池振容黼荒火三列黻三列素錦褚加帷荒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='5022:5045'>　纁紐六齊五采五貝黼翣二黻翣二畫翣二皆戴圭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='5045:5068'>　魚躍拂池君纁戴六纁披六此諸侯禮也禮器曰天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='5068:5091'>　子八翣諸侯六翣大夫四翣漢禮器制度飾棺天子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='5091:5111'>　龍火黼黻皆五列又有龍翣二其戴皆加璧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='5111:5119'>○衣翣柳之材</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='5119:5142'>　註曰必先纒衣其材乃以張飾也柳之言聚諸飾之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='5142:5169'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-15a' );" name="005-15a" class="pb">[005-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='5169:5192'>　所聚　疏曰鄭喪大記註引漢禮翣方扇以木為匡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='5192:5215'>　廣二尺兩角髙二尺四寸柄長五尺以布覆之柳即</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='5215:5229'>　帷荒是也　衣于既反註同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='5229:5237'>掌凡内之縫事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='5237:5261'>○染人掌染絲帛凡染春㬥練夏纁𤣥秋染夏冬獻功</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='5261:5285'>　註曰㬥練練其素而㬥之鄭司農云纁謂絳也𤣥謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='5285:5310'>　纁𤣥者謂始可以染此色者𤣥纁者天地之色以為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='5310:5333'>　祭服石染當及盛夏熱潤始湛研之三月而後可用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='5333:5360'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-15b' );" name="005-15b" class="pb">[005-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='5360:5384'>　考工記鍾氏則染纁術也染𤣥則史傳闕矣染夏者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='5384:5414'>　染五色謂之夏者其色以夏狄為飾禹貢曰羽<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0850' title='KR0850' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0850.png'/>夏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='5414:5444'>　狄是其總名其類有六曰翬曰搖曰<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1319' title='KR1319' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1319.png'/>曰甾曰希曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='5444:5467'>　蹲其毛羽五色皆備成章染者擬以為深淺之度是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='5467:5476'>　以放而取名焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='5476:5482'>掌凡染事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='5482:5505'>　史直翁曰天下之染必因草木土石而成先王取其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='5505:5528'>　色以配四時之宜以定上下之分皆所以為禮然先</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='5528:5555'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-16a' );" name="005-16a" class="pb">[005-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='5555:5579'>　王取色以為禮後世因色以起妄故𫝊曰五色令人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='5579:5602'>　目盲使知所謂色者出于草木土石不足為吾損益</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='5602:5625'>　則目不盲而視天下之色姑以為禮設耳　㬥步卜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='5625:5653'>　反<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0850' title='KR0850' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0850.png'/>畎同<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1319' title='KR1319' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1319.png'/>音儔放方往反</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='5653:5676'>○追師掌王后之首服為副編次追衡筓為九嬪及外</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='5676:5690'>内命婦之首服以待祭祀賓客</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='5690:5714'>　註曰鄭司農云副者婦人之首服衡維持冠者𤣥謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='5714:5737'>　副之言覆所以覆首為之飾其遺象若今步繇矣服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='5737:5764'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-16b' );" name="005-16b" class="pb">[005-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='5764:5787'>　之以從王祭祀編編列髪為之其遺象若今假紒矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='5787:5810'>　服之以桑也次次第髪長短為之所謂髲髢服之以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='5810:5833'>　見王王后之燕居亦纚筓總而已追猶治也詩云追</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='5833:5856'>　琢其璋王后之衡筓皆以玉為之唯祭服有衡垂于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='5856:5879'>　副之兩旁當耳其下以紞縣瑱笄卷髪者外内命婦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='5879:5902'>　衣鞠衣展衣者服編衣緣衣者服次外内命婦非王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='5902:5925'>　祭祀賓客佐后之禮自於其家則亦降焉少牢饋食</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='5925:5948'>　禮曰主婦髲鬄衣移袂特牲饋食禮曰主婦纚筓宵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='5948:5975'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-17a' );" name="005-17a" class="pb">[005-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='5975:5998'>　衣是也昏禮女次純衣攝盛服耳主人爵弁以迎移</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='5998:6020'>　袂緣衣之袂凡諸侯夫人于其國衣服與王后同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='6020:6043'>　追丁回反下同繇音遙紒音計髲皮寄反髢大計反</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='6043:6066'>　纚所綺反縣音懸瑱他見反卷眷免反鬄大計反純</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='6066:6072'>　側其反</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='6072:6082'>喪紀共筓絰亦如之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='6082:6105'>○屨人掌王及后之服屨為赤舄黑舄赤繶黄繶青句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='6105:6111'>素屨葛屨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='6111:6138'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-17b' );" name="005-17b" class="pb">[005-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='6138:6161'>　註曰屨自明矣必連言服者著服各有屨也複下曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='6161:6184'>　舄襌下曰屨舄屨有絇有繶有純者飾也凡屨舄各</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='6184:6208'>　象其裳之色士冠禮曰𤣥端黒屨青絇繶純素積白</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='6208:6231'>　屨緇絇繶純爵弁纁屨黑絇繶純是也王吉服有九</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='6231:6255'>　舄有三等赤舄為上冕服之舄詩云王錫韓侯𤣥衮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='6255:6278'>　赤舄則諸侯與王同下有白舄黑舄王后吉服六唯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='6278:6302'>　祭服有舄𤣥舄為上褘衣之舄也下有青舄赤舄鞠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='6302:6325'>　衣以下皆屨耳句當為絇聲之誤也絇繶純者同色</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='6325:6352'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-18a' );" name="005-18a" class="pb">[005-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='6352:6375'>　今云赤繶黄繶青絇雜互言之明舃屨衆多反覆以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='6375:6398'>　見之凡舄之飾如繢之次赤繶者王黑舄之飾黄繶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='6398:6422'>　者王后𤣥舄之飾青絇者王白舄之飾言繶必有絇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='6422:6445'>　純言絇亦有繶純三者相將王及后之赤舄皆黑飾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='6445:6468'>　后之青舄白飾凡屨之飾如繡次也黄屨白飾白屨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='6468:6491'>　黑飾黑屨青飾絇謂之拘著舄屨之頭以為行戒繶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='6491:6514'>　縫中紃純緣也天子諸侯吉事皆舄其餘唯服冕衣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='6514:6537'>　翟著舄耳士爵弁纁屨黑絇繶純尊祭服之屨飾從</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='6537:6564'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-18b' );" name="005-18b" class="pb">[005-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='6564:6587'>　繢也素屨者非純吉有凶去飾者言葛屨明有用皮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='6587:6610'>　時　疏曰素屨者大祥時所服去飾也葛屨自赤舄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='6610:6633'>　以下夏則用葛為之若冬則用皮為在素屨下者欲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='6633:6656'>　見素屨亦用葛與皮也　繶於力反句音劬著服之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='6656:6679'>　著丁庶反絇音劬純章允反下同縁悦面反著舄之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='6679:6686'>　著知畧反</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='6686:6702'>辨外内命夫命婦之命屨功屨散屨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='6702:6725'>　註曰命天之命屨纁屨命婦之命屨黄屨以下功屨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='6725:6752'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-19a' );" name="005-19a" class="pb">[005-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='6752:6775'>　次命屨于孤卿大夫則白屨黑屨九嬪内子亦然世</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='6775:6798'>　婦命婦以黑屨為功屨女御士妻命屨而已士及士</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='6798:6820'>　妻謂再命受服者散屨亦謂去飾鄭志趙商問司</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='6820:6843'>　服王后六服之制目不解請圖之答曰大裘袞衣鷩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='6843:6867'>　衣毳衣絺衣𤣥衣此六服皆纁裳赤舄韋弁衣以韎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='6867:6890'>　皮弁衣以布此二弁皆素裳白舄冠弁服黑衣裳而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='6890:6915'>　黑舄冠弁𤣥端褘衣𤣥舄首服副從王見先王揄翟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='6915:6938'>　青舄首服副從王見先公闕翟赤舄首服副從王見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='6938:6965'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-19b' );" name="005-19b" class="pb">[005-19b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='6965:6988'>　羣小祀鞠衣黄屨首服編以告桑之服襢衣白屨首</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='6988:7011'>　服編以禮見王之服縁衣黑屨首服次以御于王之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='7011:7035'>　服后服六翟三等三舄𤣥青赤鞠衣以下三屨黄白</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='7035:7056'>　黒婦人質不殊裳屨舄皆同裳色也　韎音妺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='7056:7068'>凡四時之祭祀以宜服之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='7068:7091'>　註曰祭祀而有素屨散屨者惟大祥時　王光逺曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l347' data-llen='7091:7114'>　夏葛冬皮此隨時之宜吉祭用赤舄命屨之等喪祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l348' data-llen='7114:7127'>　有素屨散屨此隨事之宜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l349' data-llen='7127:7154'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-20a' );" name="005-20a" class="pb">[005-20a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l350' data-llen='7154:7177'>○夏采掌大喪以冕服復于大祖以乘車建綏復于四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l351' data-llen='7177:7180'>郊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l352' data-llen='7180:7203'>　註曰求之王平生常所有事之處乘車玉路于太廟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l353' data-llen='7203:7226'>　以冕服不出宫也四郊以綏出國門此行道也鄭司</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l354' data-llen='7226:7249'>　農云復謂始死招魂復魄大祖始祖廟也故書綏為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l355' data-llen='7249:7287'>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR2685' title='KR2685' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2685.png'/>杜子春云當為綏<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR2685' title='KR2685' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2685.png'/>非是也𤣥謂明堂位曰凡四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l356' data-llen='7287:7310'>　代之服器魯兼用之有虞氏之旂夏后氏之綏則旌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l357' data-llen='7310:7333'>　旂有是綏者當作緌字之誤也緌以旄牛尾為之綴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l358' data-llen='7333:7360'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-20b' );" name="005-20b" class="pb">[005-20b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l359' data-llen='7360:7383'>　於橦上所謂注旄于干首者王祀四郊乘玉路建大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l360' data-llen='7383:7406'>　常今以之復去其旒異之于生亦因先王有徒緌者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l361' data-llen='7406:7429'>　士冠禮及玉藻冠緌之字故書亦多作綏者今禮家</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l362' data-llen='7429:7452'>　定作㽔　疏曰復者各依命數天子則十二人各服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l363' data-llen='7452:7475'>　朝服　黄文叔曰夏采掌復無他事也特建一官者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l364' data-llen='7475:7498'>　生事盡而死事始也曾子曰而今而後吾知免夫宋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l365' data-llen='7498:7521'>　穆公曰䙷保首領以沒于地人主能保其身至此而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l366' data-llen='7521:7551'>　冢宰之責盡矣　復扶又反<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR2685' title='KR2685' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2685.png'/>音維橦直江反朝直</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l367' data-llen='7551:7578'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-21a' );" name="005-21a" class="pb">[005-21a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l368' data-llen='7578:7586'>　遙反䙷得同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l369' data-llen='7586:7609'>　朱子曰冢宰一官兼領王之膳服嬪御此最是設官</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l370' data-llen='7609:7632'>　之深意葢天下之事無重于此又曰冢宰一篇周公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l371' data-llen='7632:7655'>　輔道成王垂灋後世用意最深切處欲知三代人主</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l372' data-llen='7655:7678'>　正心誠意之學于此可見其實　坡謂自冢宰至此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l373' data-llen='7678:7701'>　六十三職或掌其要焉或専而司焉或聨而治焉則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l374' data-llen='7701:7724'>　分職之事也夫冢宰貳王經理天下而諸官所掌不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l375' data-llen='7724:7747'>　越于居處服御財賦絲麻之事嗚呼此聖人之議道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l376' data-llen='7747:7774'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-21b' );" name="005-21b" class="pb">[005-21b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l377' data-llen='7774:7797'>　自已者也夫飲食男女人之大欲存焉然等而下之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l378' data-llen='7797:7820'>　至于庶人推而進之至于公卿或有所制故不敢縱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l379' data-llen='7820:7843'>　或有所求而未必逞若王者尊為天子富有四海何</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l380' data-llen='7843:7866'>　求而不應哉何憚而不為哉以是大欲而勢足以恢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l381' data-llen='7866:7889'>　其邪心無制節謹度于以治天下國家焉吾不知其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l382' data-llen='7889:7912'>　可也周公立冢宰以綂百官以均四海而知百官之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l383' data-llen='7912:7935'>　得其綂四海之得其均其要在王身而不外也先以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l384' data-llen='7935:7958'>　宫室安其身焉次以飲食理其體焉繼以賦式節其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l385' data-llen='7958:7985'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-22a' );" name="005-22a" class="pb">[005-22a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l386' data-llen='7985:8008'>　用焉終以内宫佐其徳焉析其事則至纎至悉若無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l387' data-llen='8008:8031'>　闗于政治之要合其大則本末兼修内外交飭其至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l388' data-llen='8031:8054'>　醇至備者乎一之以大宰之權分之以小宰内宰之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l389' data-llen='8054:8077'>　任一起居一飲食一貨用一擇採進御多寡豐約用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l390' data-llen='8077:8100'>　舍去取大臣皆得與聞之而天子不得以自私女子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l391' data-llen='8100:8123'>　小人不得以竊惑而又司是官者或以徳進或以藝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l392' data-llen='8123:8146'>　揚無邪辟以蕩王心無壬人以道其惡則上知之君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l393' data-llen='8146:8169'>　就焉而益正中材之主守焉而寡過盖正心誠意之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l394' data-llen='8169:8196'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-22b' );" name="005-22b" class="pb">[005-22b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l395' data-llen='8196:8219'>　極功而天下之治本于此人主所宜深思而躬行哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l396' data-llen='8219:8233'>　　辟芳益反上知之知音智</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l397' data-llen='8233:8256'>　坡又謂有文字來首部為易而上經始于飲食下經</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l398' data-llen='8256:8279'>　始于男女皆根本于天地而推其極于世變故禮運</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l399' data-llen='8279:8302'>　究論天道人情得失死生要歸于飲食男女内則言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l400' data-llen='8302:8325'>　后王降徳兆民亦委折陳此二事之數皆與冢宰之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l401' data-llen='8325:8348'>　職不少異焉然則自羲皇以迄三古墳典微言聖聖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l402' data-llen='8348:8371'>　相授所以議道自已錫福于民舍是無大者矣深察</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l403' data-llen='8371:8398'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-23a' );" name="005-23a" class="pb">[005-23a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l404' data-llen='8398:8421'>　乎此斯為格致深體乎此斯為誠正藏恕而行斯為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l405' data-llen='8421:8444'>　齊治均平君人修之則建極有柄持為臣知之則致</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l406' data-llen='8444:8467'>　主有本末儒者辨此則講學有實義故齊宣病好貨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l407' data-llen='8467:8490'>　好色不能至王孟子教以好與民同于王何有古者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l408' data-llen='8490:8513'>　人上之所以自審聖賢之所以格非不能外此而他</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l409' data-llen='8513:8537'>　有所指也程朱𤼵太極西銘之理尊大學為入徳之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l410' data-llen='8537:8560'>　門不過欲天子至于庶人明于天性知其不容已與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l411' data-llen='8560:8583'>　不可易而安處善樂循理耳朱子曰所以為敎皆本</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l412' data-llen='8583:8610'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-23b' );" name="005-23b" class="pb">[005-23b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l413' data-llen='8610:8633'>　于人君躬行心得之餘不待求之民生日用彝倫之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l414' data-llen='8633:8656'>　之外不既明且至乎後儒詆冢宰輔王當啓以窮理</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l415' data-llen='8656:8679'>　正心此經所職皆非其要似矣然坡攷數百年中學</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l416' data-llen='8679:8703'>　者恃理横豎鮮有要領徒以搜章劀句為格致𡨕目</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l417' data-llen='8703:8726'>　端坐為誠正彼又未必能然即或能之亦何所至所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l418' data-llen='8726:8749'>　以達而進説適以激人主之厭怒隱而授經適以誤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l419' data-llen='8749:8773'>　後生若存若亡而無精明的確親切至到之效噫𤼵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l420' data-llen='8773:8796'>　口必罵漢儒豈知所執又出其下之下乎　至王于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l421' data-llen='8796:8823'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0019', 'WYG', '005-24a' );" name="005-24a" class="pb">[005-24a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l422' data-llen='8823:8833'>　王俱去聲詆音邸</span><br/>
